mean_cn: prep. 尽管，虽然；  adv. 尽管，虽然
mean_en: (also used following the noun it refers to) without being affected by something; despite something
sentence: Notwithstanding the snow, the girl is still selling the matches.
sentence_trans: 尽管下雪了，小女孩仍然在卖火柴。
word_etyma: not知道，注意 ＋ with ＋ stand站，立 ＋ ing表示行为、状态、情况及其他 → notwithstanding尽管，虽然
